data.description: Nestled in the breathtaking landscapes of Divide, Colorado, this 5-bedroom gem with an additional flex room is a true masterpiece that combines luxurious living with nature's tranquility. Boasting 4 baths, 3568 square feet of living space, an oversized, spacious 3-car garage, and a convenient workshop, this property is a perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality. Situated on a sprawling 1.4-acre wooded lot, this home provides the perfect sanctuary for those seeking a harmonious blend of elegance and natural beauty. Imagine waking up to the serene rustle of leaves and sipping your morning coffee on your private deck, surrounded by towering trees and the crisp mountain air. Step inside to discover a thoughtfully designed interior that seamlessly flows from room to room. The 5 bedrooms offer ample space for relaxation, and the additional flex room provides versatility to cater to your unique needs—a home office, gym, or cozy reading nook, the possibilities are endless. Transitioning to the heart of the home, the kitchen is equipped with state-of-the-art appliances, forming a functional haven for culinary enthusiasts. Effortless meal preparation and delightful gatherings become second nature in this inviting space. The 3-car garage ensures plenty of space for your vehicles, and is a haven for DIY enthusiasts and hobbyists alike. Whether you're a car enthusiast, an artist, or a woodworker, this property has the perfect space for you to unleash your creativity. Conveniently located in Divide, you'll enjoy easy access to outdoor adventures, hiking trails, and all the amenities the charming town has to offer. Revel in the close-knit community and relish in the unparalleled beauty of the Colorado Rockies. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your forever home! Contact us today to schedule a private tour and experience the magic of living in Divide, CO. Your mountain dream home awaits!
